<div class="container ml-auto mr-auto">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <h1 class="text-center mt-5 mb-5">
        <a href="https://stefanbohacek.online/@stefan"
          rel="me">Stefan</a>'s creative bot
        showcase <span class="text-nowrap">ðŸ¤–ðŸŽ¨</span>
      </h1>
      <p>
        This page lists all the creative bots I've made (<a href="#active-bots">{{active_bots_count}} active</a>,
        <a href="#inactive-bots">{{inactive_bots_count}} inactive</a>, {{bots_count_total}} in total), with <a
          href="https://stefanbohacek.com/blog/analyzing-fediverse-followers/">thousands of unique followers</a> across all of them. Majority of
        the bots are <a href="https://github.com/stefanbohacek/stefans-creative-bots/">open-sourced</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you want to learn more about creative botmaking, and maybe even make your
        own bot, here's a few links to get you started:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://botwiki.org/">Botwiki</a>, an online encyclopedia of creative bots and a collection of resources for making them, including the <a
            href="https://botwiki.org/resource/guide/the-definitive-guide-to-creative-botmaking/">Definitive Guide to
            Creative Botmaking</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          the <a href="https://botmakers.org/">Botmakers</a> Discourse group
        </li>
        <li>
          tutorials and descriptions of my bot projects <a href="https://stefanbohacek.com/tag/bots/">on my blog</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          and you might also enjoy my <a href="https://stefanbohacek.com/blog/twitter-bots-a-retrospective/">retrospective on Twitter bots</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        If you're enjoying following any of these bots, here's how you can <a
          href="https://stefanbohacek.com/support-my-work/">support my work</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        <em>Note: If you don't want to see occasional announcements about new bots that I've made, <a
            href="https://fedi.tips/hiding-someones-boosts-in-mastodon-without-blocking-or-muting-them/">see how to hide
            them</a>.</em>
      </p>
      <form class="fsb-prompt">
        <label class="fw-bold">Share this page from your fediverse server</label>
        <div class="fsb-input-group mb-3">
          <span class="fsb-input-group-text">https://</span>
          <input required
            type="text"
            name="fediverse-domain"
            placeholder="mastodon.social"
            class="fsb-input fsb-domain"
            aria-label="Server domain">
          <button class="fsb-button"
            type="submit"><img
              src="https://fediverse-share-button.stefanbohacek.com/fediverse-share-button/icons/mastodon.svg"
              class="fsb-icon"></span>Share</button>
        </div>
        <p class="fsb-support-note fsb-d-none">This server does not support sharing. Please visit <a
            class="fsb-support-note-link"
            target="_blank"
            href=""></a>.</p>
      </form>
      <link rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://fediverse-share-button.stefanbohacek.com/fediverse-share-button/styles.min.css">
      <script src="https://fediverse-share-button.stefanbohacek.com/fediverse-share-button/script.min.js"
        defer
        class="fsb-script"></script>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid ml-auto mr-auto mt-5 pt-5">
  {{#if bots}}
  <div id="active-bots"
    class="row list">
    {{#each active_bots}}
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-3 list-item">
      {{> bot name=this.about.name description=this.about.description
      thumbnail=this.about.thumbnail preview=this.about.preview
      about_url=this.about.about_url source_url=this.about.source_url
      links=this.about.links file=this.about.file interval=this.about.interval
      interval_human=this.about.interval_human next_run=this.about.next_run
      last_run=this.about.last_run }}
    </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <div class="container ml-auto mr-auto">
        <h2 id="inactive-bots"
          class="text-center mt-5 mb-5">Inactive bots</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row list">
    {{#each inactive_bots}}
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-3 list-item">
      {{> bot name=this.about.name description=this.about.description
      thumbnail=this.about.thumbnail preview=this.about.preview
      about_url=this.about.about_url source_url=this.about.source_url
      links=this.about.links file=this.about.file interval=this.about.interval
      interval_human=this.about.interval_human next_run=this.about.next_run
      last_run=this.about.last_run }}
    </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
  {{/if}}
  <div class="row">
    <div class="row align-items-center mx-auto mt-5 mb-5">
      <div class="col-sm-12 mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="d-inline text-center">
          <a href="https://fightfascism.neocities.org"
            class="text-decoration-none">
            <img width="100px"
              height="100px"
              loading="lazy"
              class="m-2"
              alt="Fight Fascism"
              title="Fight fascism! Design by Angus Johnston"
              src="https://stefanbohacek.com/wp-content/themes/fourtonfish/images/other/fight-fascism-square.png">
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="d-inline text-center">
          <a href="https://lifehacker.com/where-to-donate-to-help-people-fighting-for-racial-just-1843852418"
            class="text-decoration-none">
            <img width="100px"
              height="100px"
              loading="lazy"
              class="m-2"
              alt="The text 'Black Lives Matter' in all-caps, one letter per line, alternating between black text on white background and white text on black background. "
              title="Black Lives Matter logo"
              src="https://stefanbohacek.com/wp-content/themes/fourtonfish/images/other/blm.png">
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="d-inline text-center">
          <a href="https://translifeline.org/donate/"
            class="text-decoration-none">
            <img width="100px"
              height="100px"
              loading="lazy"
              class="m-2"
              alt="The text 'Trans rights are human rights' in all-caps, laid out to form a trans rights flag with alternating blue, pink, and white stripes."
              title="Support the trans community!"
              src="https://stefanbohacek.com/wp-content/themes/fourtonfish/images/other/trans-rights.jpg">
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="d-inline text-center">
          <a href="https://indieweb.org/"
            class="text-decoration-none">
            <img width="100px"
              height="100px"
              loading="lazy"
              class="m-2"
              alt="IndieWeb Camp logo consisting of stylized letters IWC and the text 'IndieWebCamp'"
              title="Support #indieweb!"
              src="https://stefanbohacek.com/wp-content/themes/fourtonfish/images/other/indiewebcamp-black.png">
